ty",landing:{title_1:"Still confused with your future?",desc_1:"Come join the Aptitude Test and get the results right away!",title_2:"What is the Aptitude Test?",desc_2:"What kind of job I should do in the future. What the subject that I should study? This aptitude test can help you answer these questions. Simply take a test by answering a series of questions",title_3:"See Your Test Results",desc_3:"At the end of the test, you will get recommendations for majors and careers that match your character.",test_now:"Take the test now",previous_test:"Previous test results"},instructions:{1:"There are 2 parts: <ol type='a'><li>Interest Tests (99 questions)</li><li>Personality Test (39 questions)</li></ol>",2:"There are no right / wrong answers, please choose the answer that best suits you",3:"There is no work deadline. But usually, this test takes about 20 minutes",4:"All questions must be answered",5:"You can't back, after starting the test",6:"After clicking 'Next' or 'Submit', you cannot change your answer",7:"The system will save each of your answers after you click the 'Next / Next' button and 'Submit / Collect'",8:"If you come out intentionally or not in the middle of a test, you can login and resume from the last page when you exit the test",9:"You need a Quipper account to be able to access this test",10:"Do sign up / login first",11:"When you are ready to take a test, click the 'Start' button",title:"Introduction to the Test",subtitle:"Aptitude Test",last:"Good luck!",good_luck:"Good luck!"},questions:{bar:{title:"Test Instructions",example:"Example",information:"Information",riasec:{page_name:"Interest",subtitle_1:"Please choose one of the scales that represent yourself from each statement",subtitle_2:'"Are you interested or want to do the work or activities below?"',answer:{1:"Strongly Agree",2:"Agree",3:"Neutral",4:"Disagree",5:"Strongly Disagree"},example:"I like to study at night"},charcs:{page_name:"Personality",subtitle_1:"Please mark each statement:",subti